class  FdoIDeactivateLongTransaction
 The FdoIDeactivateLongTransaction interface defines the DeactivateLongTransaction command, which deactivates the active long transaction where feature manipulation commands operate on it. If the active long transaction is the root long transaction, then no long transaction will be deactivated. More...
